03. 여러 개의 그래프 그리기¶

  • (1) figure Figure .
  • (2) add_subplot subplot .
Figure 함수를 통해 Figure 객체를 만든다.¶
In [26]:
fig = plt.figure()
ax1 = fig.add_subplot(2,1,1)
ax2 = fig.add_subplot(2,1,2)

x1 = np.array([0, 1, 2, 3])
y1 = np.array([13, 18, 11, 10])

x2 = np.array([0, 1, 2, 3])
y2 = np.array([32, 81, 11, 11])

ax1.plot(x1, y1)
ax2.plot(x2, y2)
plt.show()
add_subplot 메서드를 통해 그리려는 그래프 개수만큼 subplot을 만든다.¶
In [27]:
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(10,5))

ax1 = fig.add_subplot(1,3,1)
ax2 = fig.add_subplot(1,3,2)
ax3 = fig.add_subplot(1,3,3)

plt.show()
In [29]:
# plot, bar  
x = range(0, 15)
y = [ v * v for v in x ]

fig, axs = plt.subplots(2, 2, figsize=(10,10))
axs[0,0].plot(x, y, 'o')
axs[0,1].plot(x, y, '-')
axs[1,1].bar(x,y)
axs[1,1].hist(x,y)

plt.show()
sin, cos 그래프 그려보기¶
In [31]:
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

x = np.arange(0.0, 2 * np.pi, 0.1)
sin_y = np.sin(x)
cos_y = np.cos(x)

plt.figure(figsize=(10,12))
fig, axs = plt.subplots(2)
axs[0].plot(x, sin_y, 'b--')
axs[1].plot(x, cos_y, 'r--')
plt.show()

<Figure size 720x864 with 0 Axes>

03-01. 실습¶

2행 2열의 그래프를 그려보자.¶
  • 11 : sin()
  • 12 : cos() +
  • 21 : tan() +
  • 22 : arctan() +
In [36]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np

x = np.arange(0.0, 2 * np.pi, 0.1)
sin_y = np.sin(x)
cos_y = np.cos(x)
tan_y = np.tan(x)
arctan_y = np.arctan(x)

#plt.figure(figsize=(10,10))
fig, axs = plt.subplots(2,2, figsize=(10,10))
axs[0,0].plot(x, sin_y)
axs[0,1].plot(x, cos_y, 'rs')
axs[1,0].plot(x, tan_y, 'c.')
axs[1,1].plot(x, arctan_y, 'yo')

plt.show()
